headline: Intel, AMD Warn China Customers Of Months-Long CPU Delays
summary: Intel Corp. (NASDAQ:INTC) and Advanced Micro Devices Inc. (NASDAQ:AMD) are facing tightening server CPU supplies in China as booming AI infrastructure demand strains the global chip pipeline.
